1
00:00:04,209 --> 00:00:06,169
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:12,810 --> 00:00:13,946
<Default><b>Take 'em all!</b></Default>

3
00:00:13,970 --> 00:00:16,890
<Default><b>I'd rather you fight with
our weapons than those fools.</b></Default>

4
00:00:17,309 --> 00:00:18,706
<Default><b>[sponsor 02-A
(M) laughs]</b></Default>

5
00:00:18,730 --> 00:00:21,230
<Default><b>I see.
He must be a sponsor.</b></Default>

6
00:00:23,859 --> 00:00:25,939
<Default><b>That girl has already
mastered it?</b></Default>

7
00:00:26,030 --> 00:00:27,756
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] And now.
It's time to announce</b></Default>

8
00:00:27,780 --> 00:00:28,796
<Default><b>the newly formed</b></Default>

9
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:30,870
<Default><b>Team Rock Valley's
next opponent!</b></Default>

10
00:00:30,949 --> 00:00:33,159
<Default><b>- That was awfully quick.
- Yeah.</b></Default>

11
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,159
<Default><b>For their next opponent...
What's this?</b></Default>

12
00:00:36,409 --> 00:00:38,869
<Default><b>It appears several teams
have forfeited!</b></Default>

13
00:00:38,960 --> 00:00:41,015
<Default><b>You'll just have to wait
till next time!</b></Default>

14
00:00:41,039 --> 00:00:42,396
<Default><b>[crowd screaming]</b></Default>

15
00:00:42,420 --> 00:00:44,660
<Default><b>- Forfeited?
- Why would they do that?</b></Default>

16
00:00:49,420 --> 00:00:51,219
<Default><b>Clangkity clang.</b></Default>

17
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:30,200
<Default><b>[NADIA] Congrats on winning
your first fight, Rocky.</b></Default>

18
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:33,086
<Default><b>The prize money
wasn't enough?</b></Default>

19
00:02:33,110 --> 00:02:35,135
<Default><b>Boy, you must really be
strapped for cash</b></Default>

20
00:02:35,159 --> 00:02:37,159
<Default><b>if you have to
bet on yourself.</b></Default>

21
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:39,765
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
So what if I did?</b></Default>

22
00:02:39,789 --> 00:02:41,096
<Default><b>You gonna rat me out?</b></Default>

23
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:43,240
<Default><b>Your little secret
is safe with me.</b></Default>

24
00:02:43,659 --> 00:02:45,259
<Default><b>In exchange for that.</b></Default>

25
00:02:49,669 --> 00:02:50,789
<Default><b>[smiling]</b></Default>

26
00:02:51,169 --> 00:02:53,566
<Default><b>You have to spend the night
drinking with me.</b></Default>

27
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:54,630
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

28
00:02:58,139 --> 00:02:59,979
<Default><b>[exhales]
It's not half bad.</b></Default>

29
00:03:00,139 --> 00:03:02,499
<Default><b>Tastes like
a whole rukor fruit is in it.</b></Default>

30
00:03:02,599 --> 00:03:04,719
<Default><b>You can handle
a whole rukor fruit?</b></Default>

31
00:03:04,810 --> 00:03:07,770
<Default><b>Yup, I could down
a dozen glasses of that.</b></Default>

32
00:03:08,310 --> 00:03:10,479
<Default><b>Now, what info
you got for me?</b></Default>

33
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,030
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

34
00:03:13,069 --> 00:03:14,069
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

35
00:03:14,860 --> 00:03:16,220
<Default><b>Can I help you?</b></Default>

36
00:03:17,780 --> 00:03:20,580
<Default><b>Why don't we get some
fresh night air while we talk?</b></Default>

37
00:03:24,449 --> 00:03:25,960
<Default><b>Up next</b></Default>

38
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:27,799
<Default><b>a round-robin
tournament.</b></Default>

39
00:03:28,039 --> 00:03:29,265
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
That's interesting.</b></Default>

40
00:03:29,289 --> 00:03:32,379
<Default><b>Oh, are teams typically told
who their next opponent is</b></Default>

41
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:33,776
<Default><b>right after the battle?</b></Default>

42
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:36,629
<Default><b>Yes. And if the teams forfeit
like today</b></Default>

43
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,026
<Default><b>then you win by default</b></Default>

44
00:03:38,050 --> 00:03:40,526
<Default><b>and find yourself waiting
for a worthy challenger.</b></Default>

45
00:03:40,550 --> 00:03:41,615
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Makes sense.</b></Default>

46
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:44,159
<Default><b>And the reason
there were all those forfeits.</b></Default>

47
00:03:44,469 --> 00:03:46,060
<Default><b>Was because of this?</b></Default>

48
00:03:49,439 --> 00:03:51,559
<Default><b>Payback time
for beating our teams!</b></Default>

49
00:03:51,610 --> 00:03:53,729
<Default><b>Prepare to
die, bastards!</b></Default>

50
00:03:54,069 --> 00:03:55,860
<Default><b>Hold on</b></Default>

51
00:03:55,949 --> 00:03:57,086
<Default><b>these aren't your men?</b></Default>

52
00:03:57,110 --> 00:03:59,159
<Default><b>Ah.
You think so little of me.</b></Default>

53
00:04:00,659 --> 00:04:02,490
<Default><b>Source of thy power</b></Default>

54
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,015
<Default><b>- Decipher the laws of nature.
- Magic?</b></Default>

55
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:06,186
<Default><b>Let thunder strike</b></Default>

56
00:04:06,210 --> 00:04:08,810
<Default><b>each and every one of my foes
who is before me!</b></Default>

57
00:04:09,580 --> 00:04:10,740
<Default><b>All Drifa!</b></Default>

58
00:04:10,789 --> 00:04:12,800
<Default><b>Come forth
Chain Lightning!</b></Default>

59
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:15,090
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

60
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:24,239
<Default><b>That's some power!</b></Default>

61
00:04:24,810 --> 00:04:27,656
<Default><b>So, is this why enemies are
forfeiting before the fights?</b></Default>

62
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,745
<Default><b>Your enemies will do</b></Default>

63
00:04:28,769 --> 00:04:30,969
<Default><b>whatever it takes
to come out on top.</b></Default>

64
00:04:31,189 --> 00:04:34,110
<Default><b>Like how you put rukor fruit
in my drinks at the bar?</b></Default>

65
00:04:34,769 --> 00:04:35,849
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

66
00:04:36,860 --> 00:04:38,020
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

67
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:40,620
<Default><b>- Get off of me!
- [giggling]</b></Default>

68
00:04:43,449 --> 00:04:46,369
<Default><b>I pray that we don't fight
one another in the coliseum.</b></Default>

69
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:49,190
<Default><b>You're better off giving up
before that.</b></Default>

70
00:04:52,170 --> 00:04:54,959
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] The next day</b></Default>

71
00:04:55,379 --> 00:04:56,759
<Default><b>Aah!</b></Default>

72
00:05:02,509 --> 00:05:04,906
<Default><b>They ended up matching us
against some monsters</b></Default>

73
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:06,245
<Default><b>so we used
illusion magic</b></Default>

74
00:05:06,269 --> 00:05:08,206
<Default><b>to make it look
like we struggled.</b></Default>

75
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:11,269
<Default><b>And the winner is
Team Rock Valley</b></Default>

76
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:14,769
<Default><b>who defeated the three griffins
after a fierce battle!</b></Default>

77
00:05:14,939 --> 00:05:17,360
<Default><b>We're witnessing the birth
of a new star!</b></Default>

78
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:19,505
<Default><b>[CALL OUT 02-A (M)]
Nice one, Rock Valley!</b></Default>

79
00:05:19,529 --> 00:05:21,729
<Default><b>[CALL OUT 02-B (M)]
This is bullshit!</b></Default>

80
00:05:23,779 --> 00:05:26,290
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
With each victory</b></Default>

81
00:05:27,250 --> 00:05:29,016
<Default><b>And since we were using
illusion magic</b></Default>

82
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:31,600
<Default><b>to make it look like
we were struggling to win</b></Default>

83
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:34,439
<Default><b>the betting odds
just got better and better.</b></Default>

84
00:05:35,709 --> 00:05:36,896
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
The Slave Merchant said</b></Default>

85
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,355
<Default><b>this is the biggest
department store</b></Default>

86
00:05:38,379 --> 00:05:39,939
<Default><b>in the capital city.</b></Default>

87
00:05:39,970 --> 00:05:41,089
<Default><b>Happy!</b></Default>

88
00:05:41,379 --> 00:05:43,315
<Default><b>I bet we could get more armor
and weapons</b></Default>

89
00:05:43,339 --> 00:05:44,615
<Default><b>for our matches here.</b></Default>

90
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:46,720
<Default><b>Aah! Master, look!</b></Default>

91
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:48,995
<Default><b>There's lots and lots of food
here too!</b></Default>

92
00:05:49,019 --> 00:05:52,019
<Default><b>Yeah. Let's buy enough food
to last us a while.</b></Default>

93
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,326
<Default><b>We should avoid going out
at night.</b></Default>

94
00:05:54,350 --> 00:05:56,439
<Default><b>[FILO]
Yay! Let's go! Let's go!</b></Default>

95
00:05:56,689 --> 00:05:58,545
<Default><b>[JEWELRY SELLER 02-A (M)]
Savior of the Heavenly Fowl!</b></Default>

96
00:05:58,569 --> 00:06:00,110
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Or wait</b></Default>

97
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:02,336
<Default><b>should I say
Mr. Rock Valley?</b></Default>

98
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,319
<Default><b>The underdog
of the coliseum!</b></Default>

99
00:06:04,779 --> 00:06:07,096
<Default><b>Oh, yes. I thought
that I recognized you</b></Default>

100
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:09,720
<Default><b>from the sponsors section
back at the coliseum.</b></Default>

101
00:06:09,829 --> 00:06:11,829
<Default><b>Please know
I'm cheering you on!</b></Default>

102
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:14,600
<Default><b>Everything you see here
is part of my store.</b></Default>

103
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:17,629
<Default><b>I'm willing to
invest in you</b></Default>

104
00:06:17,790 --> 00:06:20,430
<Default><b>Looks like you're doing
pretty well for yourself</b></Default>

105
00:06:20,509 --> 00:06:21,985
<Default><b>And thanks for the offer</b></Default>

106
00:06:22,009 --> 00:06:24,065
<Default><b>but I don't wanna be
in your debt.</b></Default>

107
00:06:24,089 --> 00:06:25,565
<Default><b>Come on don't say that!</b></Default>

108
00:06:25,589 --> 00:06:27,076
<Default><b>You can pay me back
by giving me</b></Default>

109
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:29,576
<Default><b>joint rights to all the profits
of the land you own.</b></Default>

110
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,745
<Default><b>[Rishia and
Raphtalia gasp]</b></Default>

111
00:06:30,769 --> 00:06:33,439
<Default><b>I'm willing to let you open up
a store at most.</b></Default>

112
00:06:33,639 --> 00:06:35,206
<Default><b>Sounds like
a deal to me!</b></Default>

113
00:06:35,230 --> 00:06:38,110
<Default><b>Now please, enjoy your time
at our fine stores!</b></Default>

114
00:06:39,819 --> 00:06:43,449
<Default><b>[gasps] If I'm
not mistaken</b></Default>

115
00:06:43,649 --> 00:06:45,209
<Default><b>I should've figured.</b></Default>

116
00:06:45,569 --> 00:06:47,005
<Default><b>[RISHIA] I've heard
if he doesn't like you</b></Default>

117
00:06:47,029 --> 00:06:48,925
<Default><b>he'll drive you
out of business.</b></Default>

118
00:06:48,949 --> 00:06:51,466
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I wouldn't worry.
Well, for now at least.</b></Default>

119
00:06:51,490 --> 00:06:53,090
<Default><b>We are his customers.</b></Default>

120
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,766
<Default><b>[FILO]
Master look at this!</b></Default>

121
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:57,709
<Default><b>- [ALL] Huh?
- We just have to buy it!</b></Default>

122
00:06:58,339 --> 00:06:59,500
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

123
00:07:06,259 --> 00:07:07,259
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

124
00:07:08,350 --> 00:07:10,615
<Default><b>They announced the name
of our next opponent!</b></Default>

125
00:07:10,639 --> 00:07:12,439
<Default><b>They're fighting
us alone?</b></Default>

126
00:07:14,889 --> 00:07:16,769
<Default><b>[exhales]
That's right!</b></Default>

127
00:07:16,980 --> 00:07:19,706
<Default><b>And it's someone who wins
almost all of their fights</b></Default>

128
00:07:19,730 --> 00:07:21,570
<Default><b>or places in
the top ranks!</b></Default>

129
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:22,966
<Default><b>They're either strong</b></Default>

130
00:07:22,990 --> 00:07:25,466
<Default><b>or they have a lot of support
from their sponsor.</b></Default>

131
00:07:25,490 --> 00:07:27,005
<Default><b>Maybe a little
bit of both.</b></Default>

132
00:07:27,029 --> 00:07:29,136
<Default><b>There are more
powerful fighters than them</b></Default>

133
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,596
<Default><b>but this time I hear
they're not participating.</b></Default>

134
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:33,580
<Default><b>Well, we're not
fighting them.</b></Default>

135
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:35,435
<Default><b>So what is our
opponent's name?</b></Default>

136
00:07:35,459 --> 00:07:36,779
<Default><b>Um, let's see.</b></Default>

137
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:39,540
<Default><b>The only name that
it has listed here is Nadia.</b></Default>

138
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,920
<Default><b>Nadia?</b></Default>

139
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:43,146
<Default><b>It says here
she uses lightning magic</b></Default>

140
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:45,450
<Default><b>and fights up close
with a big harpoon!</b></Default>

141
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,720
<Default><b>Lightning? Harpoon?</b></Default>

142
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:50,026
<Default><b>- What's wrong?
- [gasping]</b></Default>

143
00:07:50,050 --> 00:07:51,890
<Default><b>Oh, it's nothing
important.</b></Default>

144
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,906
<Default><b>And listen to this.</b></Default>

145
00:07:53,930 --> 00:07:56,980
<Default><b>Due to the forfeits, this will
be the championship match.</b></Default>

146
00:07:57,269 --> 00:07:58,709
<Default><b>The championship.</b></Default>

147
00:07:59,269 --> 00:08:00,269
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

148
00:08:01,069 --> 00:08:03,439
<Default><b>Right then</b></Default>

149
00:08:03,649 --> 00:08:06,086
<Default><b>This one's gonna be
our toughest match yet.</b></Default>

150
00:08:06,110 --> 00:08:08,295
<Default><b>I say we hit the bed early
and get some rest.</b></Default>

151
00:08:08,319 --> 00:08:10,949
<Default><b>[FILO] Wait! But we still
have to eat dinner!</b></Default>

152
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:18,420
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] And now</b></Default>

153
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:20,580
<Default><b>that you've
all been waiting for!</b></Default>

154
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,605
<Default><b>This season's
championship match</b></Default>

155
00:08:22,629 --> 00:08:24,089
<Default><b>at the coliseum!</b></Default>

156
00:08:24,709 --> 00:08:27,549
<Default><b>Will the winner be the newly
formed Team Rock Valley?</b></Default>

157
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,406
<Default><b>Or the Drunken Lightning</b></Default>

158
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:31,865
<Default><b>who's consistently
one of the top-ranking fighters</b></Default>

159
00:08:31,889 --> 00:08:33,129
<Default><b>each season!</b></Default>

160
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:34,905
<Default><b>Will you bet
on the new kids</b></Default>

161
00:08:34,929 --> 00:08:37,139
<Default><b>with horrifying
10-to-1 odds</b></Default>

162
00:08:37,389 --> 00:08:38,615
<Default><b>or play it safe</b></Default>

163
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:41,769
<Default><b>and bet on the nigh-undefeated
goddess of victory!</b></Default>

164
00:08:41,980 --> 00:08:43,570
<Default><b>The choice is yours!</b></Default>

165
00:08:43,690 --> 00:08:46,820
<Default><b>It's time for our fighters
to enter the arena!</b></Default>

166
00:08:47,149 --> 00:08:50,070
<Default><b>Team Rock Valley!</b></Default>

167
00:08:50,610 --> 00:08:52,740
<Default><b>And Nadia!</b></Default>

168
00:08:53,740 --> 00:08:54,806
<Default><b>[Fan 02-A (M)]
Nadia!</b></Default>

169
00:08:54,830 --> 00:08:57,460
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

170
00:09:01,379 --> 00:09:03,750
<Default><b>- [sighs]
- Good grief</b></Default>

171
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,525
<Default><b>I warned you
to forfeit this match</b></Default>

172
00:09:05,549 --> 00:09:07,186
<Default><b>but you just
didn't listen.</b></Default>

173
00:09:07,210 --> 00:09:08,446
<Default><b>No, I heard you</b></Default>

174
00:09:08,470 --> 00:09:10,275
<Default><b>but I've got more than money
on the line</b></Default>

175
00:09:10,299 --> 00:09:12,025
<Default><b>- so I have to win.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

176
00:09:12,049 --> 00:09:14,889
<Default><b>Naofu... I mean, Rock</b></Default>

177
00:09:15,009 --> 00:09:16,889
<Default><b>Yeah, a little bit.</b></Default>

178
00:09:18,059 --> 00:09:19,219
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

179
00:09:21,850 --> 00:09:23,410
<Default><b>- [giggles]
- [gasps]</b></Default>

180
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,520
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

181
00:09:24,860 --> 00:09:25,956
<Default><b>Hey, Get off!</b></Default>

182
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:27,916
<Default><b>You're trying to get money
to buy the slaves</b></Default>

183
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:29,966
<Default><b>from Lurolona village
aren't you?</b></Default>

184
00:09:29,990 --> 00:09:31,870
<Default><b>- How kind.
- [Naofumi gasps]</b></Default>

185
00:09:33,370 --> 00:09:36,330
<Default><b>This might be a great way
to get a lot of money fast</b></Default>

186
00:09:36,950 --> 00:09:39,556
<Default><b>but I do not lose to people
who are only here to fight</b></Default>

187
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:41,596
<Default><b>in the coliseum
to get rich quick.</b></Default>

188
00:09:41,620 --> 00:09:43,500
<Default><b>Don't hold
back against her.</b></Default>

189
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:47,879
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Team Rock Valley versus Nadia!</b></Default>

190
00:09:48,419 --> 00:09:52,049
<Default><b>Let this season's
championship battle, begin!</b></Default>

191
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,429
<Default><b>Source of thy power</b></Default>

192
00:10:00,059 --> 00:10:01,939
<Default><b>Decipher the
laws of nature.</b></Default>

193
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,245
<Default><b>Don't let it hit
you directly.</b></Default>

194
00:10:04,269 --> 00:10:05,589
<Default><b>You might die!</b></Default>

195
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,920
<Default><b>Drifa. Thunder Burst!</b></Default>

196
00:10:11,690 --> 00:10:13,610
<Default><b>[Naofumi grunts]</b></Default>

197
00:10:18,620 --> 00:10:19,620
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

198
00:10:20,330 --> 00:10:22,210
<Default><b>Time for my
special attack!</b></Default>

199
00:10:22,330 --> 00:10:24,330
<Default><b>Huh? Source of thy power</b></Default>

200
00:10:24,419 --> 00:10:26,476
<Default><b>I order thee.
Decipher the laws of nature.</b></Default>

201
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,816
<Default><b>You're going down, lady!</b></Default>

202
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:30,629
<Default><b>Lightning, become a power
which protects me!</b></Default>

203
00:10:30,710 --> 00:10:32,919
