208
00:10:43,980 --> 00:10:45,600
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

209
00:10:47,809 --> 00:10:49,129
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

210
00:10:49,769 --> 00:10:51,005
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Amazing!</b></Default>

211
00:10:51,029 --> 00:10:52,836
<Default><b>The two sides
