214
00:10:57,870 --> 00:11:00,580
<Default><b>that temporarily submerges
the entire area.</b></Default>

215
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,620
<Default><b>They want me
to put on a good show.</b></Default>

216
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,120
<Default><b>What?
How the hell's that fair?</b></Default>

217
00:11:06,289 --> 00:11:08,476
<Default><b>You have to give the people
what they want, don't you?</b></Default>

218
00:11:08,500 --> 00:11:10,820
<Default><b>It's time for me
to take this seriously.</b></Default>

219
00:11:11,169 --> 00:11:12,169
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

220
00:11:12,460 --> 00:11:14,299
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

221
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:17,655
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Hang on tight, folks!</b></Default>

222
00:11:17,679 --> 00:11:20,025
<Default><b>It looks like
Nadia is about to transform.</b></Default>

223
00:11:20,049 --> 00:11:21,245
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
"Transform?"</b></Default>

224
00:11:21,269 --> 00:11:24,349
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] Try not to get
