227
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:36,360
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Is that
a killer whale Demi-human?</b></Default>

228
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:38,310
<Default><b>Here I come!</b></Default>

229
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,830
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

230
00:11:43,909 --> 00:11:46,000
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- Shigaraki! -Sis!</b></Default>

231
00:11:47,330 --> 00:11:49,090
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Run! You'll die!</b></Default>

232
00:11:49,460 --> 00:11:51,879
<Default><b>Is that you? Sadeena?</b></Default>

233
00:12:00,889 --> 00:12:02,809
<Default><b>- Oh, my?
- [both gasping]</b></Default>

234
00:12:03,429 --> 00:12:04,989
