235
00:12:05,059 --> 00:12:06,499
<Default><b>It really is you.</b></Default>

236
00:12:07,309 --> 00:12:09,109
<Default><b>It is you, right,
Sadeena?</b></Default>

237
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:11,600
<Default><b>If you're calling me
by that name then</b></Default>

238
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:15,149
<Default><b>that means.
