239
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:17,659
<Default><b>Yes, I am.
I can't believe it.</b></Default>

240
00:12:17,899 --> 00:12:19,005
<Default><b>It's really you!</b></Default>

241
00:12:19,029 --> 00:12:21,120
