What's wrong?</b></Default>

247
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:32,700
<Default><b>[NADIA] Uh.</b></Default>

248
00:12:36,669 --> 00:12:37,989
<Default><b>Sadeena, wait!</b></Default>

249
00:12:40,179 --> 00:12:42,155
<Default><b>[NADIA] You were gathering up
