256
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:02,770
<Default><b>Sadeena's a Demi-human
she can take it.</b></Default>

257
00:13:03,330 --> 00:13:04,410
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

258
00:13:04,830 --> 00:13:06,159
<Default><b>Here I go!</b></Default>

259
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:11,460
<Default><b>Zweit Tornado!</b></Default>

260
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:14,210
