272
00:14:05,889 --> 00:14:07,689
<Default><b>I'll deal with
that issue.</b></Default>

273
00:14:08,519 --> 00:14:09,905
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] The winner
of the championship</b></Default>

274
00:14:09,929 --> 00:14:11,529
<Default><b>is none other than...</b></Default>

275
00:14:12,019 --> 00:14:15,610
