276
00:14:16,570 --> 00:14:18,399
<Default><b>S-Sorry, folks</b></Default>

277
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,125
<Default><b>but it seems
the sponsors have declared</b></Default>

278
00:14:20,149 --> 00:14:21,836
<Default><b>that this
final championship battle</b></Default>

279
00:14:21,860 --> 00:14:23,620
<Default><b>will be
declared invalid.</b></Default>

280
00:14:23,700 --> 00:14:24,900
<Default><b>Wait, what?</b></Default>

281
00:14:25,029 --> 00:14:27,306
<Default><b>Instead, there will be
an exhibition match</b></Default>

282
00:14:27,330 --> 00:14:29,476
<Default><b>between the two fighters
who participated</b></Default>

283
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:30,726
