284
00:14:30,750 --> 00:14:33,350
<Default><b>who has yet to make
an appearance here with us!</b></Default>

285
00:14:33,539 --> 00:14:35,169
<Default><b>- Oh, my.
- Damn it.</b></Default>

286
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:37,316
<Default><b>Your sponsor's a real pain
in the ass.</b></Default>

287
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:39,180
<Default><b>I understand
his reasoning.</b></Default>

288
00:14:39,460 --> 00:14:40,645
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
So now...</b></Default>

289
00:14:40,669 --> 00:14:43,129
<Default><b>Team Rockvalley
