290
00:14:43,259 --> 00:14:45,379
<Default><b>in order to
wage a war against...</b></Default>

291
00:14:52,980 --> 00:14:55,850
<Default><b>Careful, Rocky</b></Default>

292
00:14:56,309 --> 00:14:57,995
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
The clown is dangerous?</b></Default>

293
00:14:58,019 --> 00:14:59,690
<Default><b>[gasps] That's them!</b></Default>

294
00:14:59,899 --> 00:15:03,190
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] Their opponent is
the Murder Clown!</b></Default>

295
00:15:03,529 --> 00:15:05,635
<Default><b>Betting will be available
for the first 10 minutes</b></Default>

296
00:15:05,659 --> 00:15:07,216
<Default><b>after the match starts.</b></Default>

297
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,306
<Default><b>And we will be
