298
00:15:09,330 --> 00:15:11,130
<Default><b>for the finals
right away!</b></Default>

299
00:15:11,450 --> 00:15:13,306
<Default><b>So we have to fight
the clown, huh?</b></Default>

300
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:16,750
<Default><b>Indeed. We can worry about
everything else after we win!</b></Default>

301
00:15:17,210 --> 00:15:21,340
<Default><b>Ladies and gentlemen</b></Default>

302
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,395
<Default><b>I'll end this quickly!</b></Default>

303
00:15:23,419 --> 00:15:25,470
<Default><b>Here I go.
Instant Blade Mist!</b></Default>

304
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:28,480
<Default><b>[MURDER CLOWN]
Spider Net.</b></Default>

305
00:15:29,389 --> 00:15:30,429
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

306
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,320
<Default><b>[MURDER CLOWN]
Bind Wire.</b></Default>

307
00:15:33,559 --> 00:15:35,389
<Default><b>- [gasps]
- The hell?</b></Default>

308
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:37,309
<Default><b>[groans]
It's too strong!</b></Default>

309
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,720
<Default><b>- Damn!
- Hey, Rocky</b></Default>

310
00:15:51,909 --> 00:15:54,549
<Default><b>cast a choral spell with me
and we can end this!</b></Default>

311
00:15:54,659 --> 00:15:56,939
<Default><b>Sorry, but I've never cast a...
[gasps]</b></Default>

312
00:15:57,830 --> 00:16:00,310
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Is it like what Ost
did back then?</b></Default>

313
00:16:00,590 --> 00:16:02,476
<Default><b>[NADIA]
There's no time to hesitate!</b></Default>

314
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:05,100
<Default><b>Your Birdie and Raphtalia
are counting on this!</b></Default>

315
00:16:05,340 --> 00:16:06,340
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

316
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:09,970
<Default><b>Two powers, imbued with
strength to give them succor.</b></Default>

317
00:16:10,470 --> 00:16:12,639
<Default><b>Strength to overcome
destined defeat</b></Default>

318
00:16:12,850 --> 00:16:15,050
<Default><b>and lead them
to a victorious future.</b></Default>

319
00:16:15,269 --> 00:16:16,615
<Default><b>- [NADIA] Dragon Vein.
- [NAOFUMI] Dragon Vein.</b></Default>

320
00:16:16,639 --> 00:16:18,875
<Default><b>[BOTH] We ask you to hear
our desperate wish!</b></Default>

321
00:16:18,899 --> 00:16:21,269
<Default><b>[BOTH] Source
of thy power</b></Default>

322
00:16:21,610 --> 00:16:23,206
<Default><b>[BOTH] Decipher the laws
of nature</b></Default>

323
00:16:23,230 --> 00:16:24,255
<Default><b>and grant me the power</b></Default>

324
00:16:24,279 --> 00:16:26,439
<Default><b>to overcome
the obstacles before me!</b></Default>

325
00:16:28,029 --> 00:16:29,069
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

326
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:31,950
<Default><b>Oh, my. So then that's
the kind of spell we get.</b></Default>

327
00:16:32,279 --> 00:16:34,370
