Descent of the Thunder God!</b></Default>

328
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:39,750
<Default><b>Hey, Rocky, Just so we're
on the same page</b></Default>

329
00:16:39,919 --> 00:16:41,645
<Default><b>you know
who our target is, right?</b></Default>

330
00:16:41,669 --> 00:16:42,669
<Default><b>Yeah!</b></Default>

331
00:16:45,419 --> 00:16:47,019
<Default><b>[Raphtalia screaming]</b></Default>

332
00:16:47,419 --> 00:16:48,459
<Default><b>Sister.</b></Default>

333
00:16:51,179 --> 00:16:52,720
<Default><b>[gasps] Huh!</b></Default>

334
00:16:55,139 --> 00:16:56,259
<Default><b>Raphtalia</b></Default>

335
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:59,809
<Default><b>we gave you
a choral spell</b></Default>

336
00:17:00,940 --> 00:17:03,190
<Default><b>- Got it!
- I won't lose.</b></Default>

337
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:14,410
<Default><b>It's over.
Brave Blade: Mist!</b></Default>

338
00:17:16,039 --> 00:17:17,719
<Default><b>[Murder Clown groaning]</b></Default>

339
00:17:18,200 --> 00:17:19,200
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

340
00:17:31,130 --> 00:17:32,446
<Default><b>You're finished!</b></Default>

341
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:35,390
<Default><b>Fusion Technique.
Blade of the Thunder Emperor!</b></Default>

342
00:17:35,970 --> 00:17:37,809
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

343
00:17:50,279 --> 00:17:51,319
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

344
00:18:01,619 --> 00:18:02,659
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

345
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:05,200
<Default><b>- [MURDER CLOWN] Scape Doll.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

346
00:18:05,329 --> 00:18:06,750
