351
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:20,260
<Default><b>Your base strength
is far too low.</b></Default>

352
00:18:20,599 --> 00:18:21,719
<Default><b>Say what?</b></Default>

353
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,495
<Default><b>[MURDER CLOWN]
Unless you're a hero</b></Default>

354
00:18:23,519 --> 00:18:25,359
<Default><b>no one can
stand up against</b></Default>

355
00:18:25,599 --> 00:18:27,919
