trouble with me.</b></Default>

357
00:18:31,150 --> 00:18:33,795
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What in the world
is she talking about?</b></Default>

358
00:18:33,819 --> 00:18:35,845
<Default><b>[MURDER CLOWN]
I fought enough to earn my pay.</b></Default>

359
00:18:35,869 --> 00:18:38,709
<Default><b>Therefore, there is no reason
to continue this fight.</b></Default>

360
00:18:39,039 --> 00:18:40,519
<Default><b>Let us meet again.</b></Default>

361
00:18:42,079 --> 00:18:44,079
<Default><b>Try not to get
yourself killed.</b></Default>

362
00:18:45,670 --> 00:18:47,750
<Default><b>A clown who's
also a ninja?</b></Default>

363
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:51,380
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)] Um. It seems
Murder Clown has disappeared!</b></Default>

364
00:18:51,759 --> 00:18:53,509
