395
00:20:04,079 --> 00:20:05,515
<Default><b>Which means
it all worked out</b></Default>

396
00:20:05,539 --> 00:20:08,210
<Default><b>- right, Master Naofumi?
- Hip-hip Hooray!</b></Default>

397
00:20:08,670 --> 00:20:11,000
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

398
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:13,660
<Default><b>- It's good to see you again.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

399
00:20:15,589 --> 00:20:18,430
<Default><b>You too, Sadeena.
[smiles]</b></Default>

400
00:20:20,339 --> 00:20:21,899
<Default><b>My how you've grown.</b></Default>

401
00:20:22,390 --> 00:20:23,906
<Default><b>I'm glad to
see you're safe.</b></Default>

402
00:20:23,930 --> 00:20:26,349
<Default><b>I can't believe it.
It really is you.</b></Default>

403
00:20:26,890 --> 00:20:28,170
<Default><b>I'm so happy.</b></Default>

404
00:20:28,519 --> 00:20:29,759
<Default><b>I really am.</b></Default>

405
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:32,745
<Default><b>I heard rumors
that the Shield Hero</b></Default>

406
00:20:32,769 --> 00:20:35,545
<Default><b>had one of the Lurolona Village
Demi-humans with him.</b></Default>

407
00:20:35,569 --> 00:20:37,449
<Default><b>I never thought
it'd be you!</b></Default>

408
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,450
<Default><b>Let's start over.
I'm Sadeena!</b></Default>

409
00:20:41,529 --> 00:20:43,119
<Default><b>I'm Naofumi Iwatani.</b></Default>

410
00:20:43,660 --> 00:20:45,055
<Default><b>Nice to meet you.</b></Default>

411
00:20:45,079 --> 00:20:47,479
<Default><b>And thank you
for watching over Raphtalia.</b></Default>

412
00:20:48,039 --> 00:20:49,199
<Default><b>Now please</b></Default>

413
00:20:49,329 --> 00:20:51,710
<Default><b>take care of me
the same way, Naofumi.</b></Default>

414
00:20:52,039 --> 00:20:53,119
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

415
00:21:04,720 --> 00:21:07,730
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

416
00:21:16,109 --> 00:21:17,585
<Default><b>Oh, hey, there Fohl</b></Default>

417
00:21:17,609 --> 00:21:19,249
<Default><b>do you want the usual?</b></Default>

418
00:21:26,579 --> 00:21:27,979
<Default><b>[coins clinking]</b></Default>

419
00:21:28,369 --> 00:21:31,369
<Default><b>I hope that you're able to
get them better medicine soon.</b></Default>

420
00:21:31,579 --> 00:21:33,139
<Default><b>Here, take this too.</b></Default>

421
00:21:40,130 --> 00:21:42,009
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

422
00:21:53,599 --> 00:21:55,400
<Default><b>Atla, I'm back.</b></Default>

423
00:21:56,319 --> 00:21:57,439
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

424
00:22:00,200 --> 00:22:02,990
<Default><b>[ATLA] Oh, good.
Welcome back, brother.</b></Default>

